headline: Best Buy Appoints Meghan Frank to Board of Directors
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 12, 2025--Best Buy Co., Inc. (NYSE: BBY) has appointed Meghan Frank, a leading global retail and finance executive, to its Board of Directors, effective immediately.
